layout: layouts/element.njk
title: "svg"
description: "The SVG element embeds scalable vector graphics with size variants, color options, and built-in animations for icons and illustrations."
elementName: svg
category: native
nativeGroup: Embedded
currentPath: /docs/elements/native/svg/
permalink: /docs/elements/native/svg/
